-- MAN SE Denies Newspaper Report That Volkswagen's Heizmann to Become Chief
-- Andreas Cremer
-- 2010-06-21T08:23:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/man-se-denies-newspaper-report-that-volkswagen-s-heizmann-to-become-chief.html

          
          
             MAN SE denied a Bild newspaper
report that Volkswagen AG’s production chief Jochem Heizmann
will become the truckmaker’s chief executive officer, said MAN
spokesman Dominique Nadelhofer. Speculation about a CEO change
is “completely unfounded,” Nadelhofer told Bloomberg News.  
